pH of the soil ranges from 5.49 to 6.13 ,
 Electrical Conductivity ranges from 0.059 to 0.306 ,
 Organic Carbon  ranges from 0.52 to 1.49 ,
 Phosphorus ranges from 6 to 10.5 ,
 Potassium ranges from 29.D112 to 40.04 ,
 Sulphur values can be 2, 3, or 4 ,
 Boron varies from 0.012 to 0.087 ,
 Therefore, adding or reducing fertilizers to the soil after studying above nutritional values crops like paddy, maize and barley can be grown.
